"title": "6218: provoking God",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "6218",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The arousing of God's righteous anger in response to the sin of his people, particularly their idolatry.</p>\n<h2>God is provoked by sin and disobedience</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut9:7-Deut9:8\">DEU 9:7–9:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num32:9-Num32:13\">NUM 32:9–32:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut31:29\">DEU 31:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh7:1\">JOS 7:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam6:6-2Sam6:7\">2SA 6:6–6:7</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr13:9-1Chr13:10\">1CH 13:9–13:10</a> <em>Uzzah's disobedience in touching the ark cost him his life</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam24:1\">2SA 24:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs15:30\">1KI 15:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs16:2-1Kgs16:3\">1KI 16:2–16:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs16:7\">1KI 16:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs21:21-1Kgs21:22\">1KI 21:21–21:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs21:14-2Kgs21:15\">2KI 21:14–21:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa65:1-Isa65:5\">ISA 65:1–65:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer32:30-Jer32:33\">JER 32:30–32:33</a></p>\n<h2>God is provoked by the rejection of his chosen leaders and prophets</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr36:15-2Chr36:16\">2CH 36:15–36:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num12:1\">NUM 12:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num12:9\">NUM 12:9</a></p>\n<h2>God is provoked by injustice</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod22:22-Exod22:24\">EXO 22:22–22:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa59:15-Isa59:18\">ISA 59:15–59:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek8:17\">EZK 8:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos12:14\">HOS 12:14</a></p>\n<h2>God is provoked by complaining</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num11:1\">NUM 11:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod4:10-Exod4:14\">EXO 4:10–4:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num11:4-Num11:10\">NUM 11:4–11:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num11:33\">NUM 11:33</a></p>\n<h2>God is provoked by idolatry</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:25-Deut4:26\">DEU 4:25–4:26</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:26\">EZK 16:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut9:16-Deut9:19\">DEU 9:16–9:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg2:12-Judg2:13\">JDG 2:12–2:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg3:5-Judg3:8\">JDG 3:5–3:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs14:9\">1KI 14:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs14:15\">1KI 14:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs16:13\">1KI 16:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs16:26\">1KI 16:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs16:33\">1KI 16:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs22:53\">1KI 22:53</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:11\">2KI 17:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs22:17\">2KI 22:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs23:25-2Kgs23:27\">2KI 23:25–23:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr28:25\">2CH 28:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:58-Ps78:59\">PSA 78:58–78:59</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps106:28-Ps106:29\">PSA 106:28–106:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer7:17-Jer7:19\">JER 7:17–7:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer8:19\">JER 8:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer25:6-Jer25:7\">JER 25:6–25:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer44:3\">JER 44:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer44:8\">JER 44:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek20:28\">EZK 20:28</a></p>\n<h2>God is provoked by human sacrifice</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:17\">2KI 17:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs21:6\">2KI 21:6</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr33:6\">2CH 33:6</a></p>",
